{"tid":1603073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"9月29號抗極權悉尼遊行報告","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:50:50.000Z","uid":22342,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a5913d2d714389b1a0a0fd41be7b01705b0130c6","tid":1603073,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"9月29號<br />\n人數：3000人<br />\n下午1點鐘 state library of NSW<br />\n大家出奇地早到， 所以準備開始摺紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYTtOje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYTtOje.jpg&h=2dab8ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午1點50分 state library of NSW<br />\n開始好多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGrftg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGrftg1.jpg&h=30fd1411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yseHSQ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyseHSQ1.jpg&h=b4ae30b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下午2點10分 state library of NSW<br />\n原先兩點鐘出發但係我哋太多人所以澳警用咗十分鐘開路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uj4s3Tg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUj4s3Tg.jpg&h=c401143a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始出發<br />\n<br />\n下午兩點三十分 Martin place<br />\n去到martin Place，因為有梯級，搞手叫大家行慢少少，後生仔扶一扶老人家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dK8Njs8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdK8Njs8.jpg&h=5553cb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午三點 town hall<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Cz46cg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Cz46cg.jpg&h=4195a488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbukExi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbukExi.jpg&h=b2450007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROQoCi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROQoCi1.jpg&h=a1fe5354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6tcKmLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6tcKmLH.jpg&h=30852b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cy9wMco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcy9wMco.jpg&h=c19ba0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axCRMcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxCRMcq.jpg&h=ade4d4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G23Njxs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG23Njxs.jpg&h=5e070497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eynircu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEynircu.jpg&h=34dd3bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZVcvEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZVcvEb.jpg&h=38fc424c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4點 Town Hall<br />\n臨完場前，多謝澳洲警察幫手維持秩序，澳洲警察表示：紅都面曬<br />\n<br />\n4點 唔知幾多分 Town Hall<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKLjVaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKLjVaf.jpg&h=eb5cc6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突發，兩個hehe喺度做埋啲gay 嘢<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n有張red object就跌咗落地下，然後咁啱玩緊London bridge is falling down<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/dXdMseibCG4HUCw1oj/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FdXdMseibCG4HUCw1oj%2Fgiphy.gif&h=89100991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時亦都有舞旗手出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/MCpIkQDEfxDvTOlk1W/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FMCpIkQDEfxDvTOlk1W%2Fgiphy.gif&h=37edea0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更多相請到<a href=\"https://t.me/sydneyantiextraditionlawreminder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsydneyantiextraditionlawreminder&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrWXO